HEADWORD: disconcerting
<hw>disconcerting</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>hard to deal with; causing
uncertainty or confusion about how to act or react.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> awkward, embarrassing, off-putting, sticky, tight,
unenviable.</syn>⟦br⟧
